than a hurried Saturday on a packed high street \u2014 it deserves a calm boutique, a glass of something chilled and a team who genuinely cares.</p>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "a802908", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "e72ae97", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section class=\"section band-ivory2\"><div class=\"container split\">\n<div class=\"framed reveal\"><img alt=\"Veni Infantino floral appliqu\u00e9 designer wedding gown\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"__WTB_BASE__/assets/veni-4.webp\"/></div>\n<div class=\"reveal\"><span class=\"eyebrow\">What Bolton Brides Love</span><h2>Designer Gowns, Without The Crush</h2><span class=\"divider left\"></span><p>We're an official stockist of <strong>Sophia Tolli</strong>, <strong>Veni Infantino</strong>, <strong>Phoenix Gowns</strong> and <strong>White Rose</strong> \u2014 from soft romantic lace to bold statement shapes, with plus-size collections that flatter every figure. Over 200 gowns, one unhurried appointment, all eyes on you.</p><div class=\"card-tags\"><span class=\"tag\">Private Appointments</span><span class=\"tag\">Plus Size Bridal</span><span class=\"tag\">200+ Gowns In Store</span></div></div>\n</div></section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "509a76e", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom"